{"tid":631195,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【靈魂出竅?】《櫻桃小丸子》罕見擺烏龍 同框驚現兩個嫲嫲","createTime":"2018-04-16T08:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T04:35:44.000Z","uid":49391,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aed9a30766fa01abab161bf6f63b5582b7f8d9c8","tid":631195,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180416/large/1523846826_d9e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F1523846826_d9e8.jpg&h=9d1d207b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【新增回應】<br />\n富士電視台嘅長壽電視動畫《櫻桃小丸子》，從90年代播到o依家，可謂橫跨咗幾代嘅觀眾，絕對係大人細路嘅美好回憶。<br />\n<br />\n不過，《櫻桃小丸子》噚日喺日本播出嘅最新一集卻發生「靈異事件」，唔少觀眾都發現同一個畫面竟然同時間出現兩個嫲嫲，繼而引起網民喺社交網洗板式討論。<br />\n呢集劇情交代到小丸子一家爭睇電視，本來坐低嘅嫲嫲就起身行埋電視機轉台，點知鏡頭一轉，嫲嫲企喺電視旁邊嘅同時，原位仍然見到另一個嫲嫲坐喺度，仲同其他家人一樣，對「自己」轉台呢個舉動用滴汗來表達出無奈之情。其實出現兩個嫲嫲，好明顯係製作單位出現罕見嘅擺烏龍情況，由於日本節目甚少出現呢類致命性嘅失誤，唔少網民都議論紛紛，有人疑問係咪刻意加入嘅恐怖元素，亦有指劇情可能交代嫲嫲一直係對「孖妹」，仲話佢可能識得靈魂出竅。<br />\n及至今日，電視台方面對於今次失誤已作出道歉，並回應指係作畫上出錯，表示今後製作時會加倍注意。<br />\n精選娛聞，喺晒《娛果》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180416/58079001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F58079001&d=B3wWFzDYCiY6GGcomhzFmr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=e7c0674d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F58079001&h=946b3c02\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180416/58079001</a>"},{"pid":"d5dd21cd9308d0e049e3ec0908dd20da3715db80","tid":631195,"uid":69083,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"咁爺爺咪晚晚玩 一皇兩后<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10154a4f25c65d0d904e5fd3d2f3f8f7a7662013","tid":631195,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"影分身"},{"pid":"9a0cd1758804001d754e576be3dd414559e50a28","tid":631195,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:02:30.000Z","msg":"崩壞姐"},{"pid":"a306575933637325b180d620976633d75c36c6c5","tid":631195,"uid":82404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"整錯咪整錯囉<br />\n可以ff到咁多野出來"},{"pid":"796cf9c1b45da58f554d18b682e0e2fa9bdaf485","tid":631195,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"成家人見到個假嫲嫲，所以咪滴哂汗囉"},{"pid":"a84b701220fe456c6027935f6b03cf1ab506fc2c","tid":631195,"uid":5188,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/182633_1ee4102e23ee5df23545278a9eba3b32.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F182633_1ee4102e23ee5df23545278a9eba3b32.png&h=7e6e6cc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/182633_875bff618be81a0df68b565dde048d06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F182633_875bff618be81a0df68b565dde048d06.png&h=04df198d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁transformers 要道歉幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d486ec9e856860e3aefc32bbe69e39219a468adf","tid":631195,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a84b701220fe456c6027935f6b03cf1ab506fc2c","tid":631195,"uid":5188,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/182633_1ee4102e23ee5df23545278a9eba3b32.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F182633_1ee4102e23ee5df23545278a9eba3b32.png&h=7e6e6cc6&s={SIZE}\" /